### HEALTH CHECK - VERIFY THE GAME SERVICE IS RUNNING
GET http://localhost:4001/health

### CREATE ROUND - OPEN A BETTING ROUND FOR MANUAL TESTING
POST http://localhost:4001/games/rounds
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roundId": "round-rmq-1"
}

### GET CURRENT ROUND - CONFIRM THE ROUND IS IN BETTING PHASE
GET http://localhost:4001/games/rounds/current

### GET ROUNDS HISTORY - LIST FINISHED ROUNDS
GET http://localhost:4001/games/rounds/history?page=1&limit=20

### PLACE BET - BET INTO THE CURRENT BETTING ROUND
POST http://localhost:4001/games/bet
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-rmq-1",
  "betId": "bet-rmq-1",
  "amountCents": "250"
}

### START CURRENT ROUND - CLOSE BETTING AND BEGIN MULTIPLIER RUN
POST http://localhost:4001/games/rounds/current/start

### GET CURRENT ROUND - CONFIRM THE ROUND IS RUNNING
GET http://localhost:4001/games/rounds/current

### CASHOUT BET - CASH OUT THE PLAYER BET DURING THE RUNNING PHASE
POST http://localhost:4001/games/bet/cashout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": "player-rmq-1"
}

### GET MY BETS HISTORY - TEMPORARY PLAYER ID UNTIL JWT AUTH BLOCK
GET http://localhost:4001/games/bets/me?playerId=player-rmq-1&page=1&limit=20

### CRASH CURRENT ROUND - STOP THE MULTIPLIER AT THE CRASH POINT
POST http://localhost:4001/games/rounds/current/crash

### SETTLE CURRENT ROUND - MARK REMAINING PLACED BETS AS LOST
POST http://localhost:4001/games/rounds/current/settle

### VERIFY ROUND - REVEAL SERVER SEED AND CHECK PROVABLY FAIR RESULT
GET http://localhost:4001/games/rounds/round-rmq-1/verify

### GET CURRENT ROUND - CHECK 404 OR NEXT BETTING ROUND AFTER SETTLEMENT
GET http://localhost:4001/games/rounds/current
